devdoc.details: A DeFi-powered savings platform for financial inclusion on Celo

closeGoal(uint256).details: Close a savings goal and withdraw all funds

params._goalId: Index of the goal to close

deposit(uint256).details: Deposit funds into a specific savings goal

params._goalId: Index of the goal to deposit into

getGoal(address,uint256).details: Get a specific goal for a user

getGoalCount(address).details: Get the number of goals for a user

getGoalProgress(address,uint256).details: Get progress percentage for a goal

getTotalSavings(address).details: Get total savings for a user across all goals

getUserGoals(address).details: Get all goals for a user

isGoalCompleted(address,uint256).details: Check if a goal has reached its target

withdraw(uint256,uint256).details: Withdraw funds from a specific savings goal

params._goalId: Index of the goal to withdraw from
